Package: bison
Section: devel
Priority: optional
Architecture: ARCH
Depends: libfl-dev, libz-dev, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: YACC-compatible parser generator
 Bison is a general-purpose parser generator that converts 
 an annotated context-free grammar into a deterministic LR 
 or generalized LR (GLR) parser employing LALR(1) parser 
 tables.
 .
 This package provides bison, liby.a, examples and m4 macros 
 required by bison at runtime.

Package: bison-doc
Section: doc
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Recommends: man-db, info
Depends: bison (= ${binary:Version})
Description: documentation for bison
 This package provides info and manpages for bison
